00:39:27.956 --> 00:39:31.003
[voice continues
whispering, faint]

604
00:39:32.352 --> 00:39:33.571
Who's there?

605
00:39:33.614 --> 00:39:37.662
[multiple voices
whispering, faint]

606
00:39:39.054 --> 00:39:41.013
Hello?

607
00:39:41.056 --> 00:39:42.449
Hello!

608
00:39:44.103 --> 00:39:45.583
Who's there?

609
00:39:45.626 --> 00:39:47.759
[man, muffled]
Shut up![thumping on floor]

