676
00:44:47.145 --> 00:44:49.625
Are you sure
about that? What does that mean?

677
00:44:49.669 --> 00:44:51.497
Nothing.
I'm... I'm just asking.

678
00:44:51.540 --> 00:44:53.847
As I said,
I'd like this interview to be about you.

679
00:44:53.891 --> 00:44:57.503
I answered your question, so...
salvation.

