696
00:45:48.554 --> 00:45:51.122
Well, I'm glad you approve.

697
00:45:51.165 --> 00:45:53.994
On the other hand... On the other hand,
what?

698
00:45:54.038 --> 00:45:56.431
On the other hand,
it's the only product I can think of

699
00:45:56.475 --> 00:45:59.260
