712
00:46:32.728 --> 00:46:35.819
Okay, but really, after this,
we have to move on.

713
00:46:35.862 --> 00:46:37.168
Okay.

714
00:46:39.474 --> 00:46:42.173
Okay, well,
uh, the instructions.

715
00:46:43.565 --> 00:46:46.481
